  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK941">
<l>mikiṉuṅ kuṟaiyiṉu nōy ceyyu nūlōr</l>
<l>vaḷimutalā eṇṇiya mūṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If (food and work are either) excessive or deficient, the three things enumerated by (medical) writers, flatulence, biliousness, and phlegm, will cause (one) disease.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
